{"tid":1014561,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"不見天日 艾斯高：我都係想踢波 點解唔畀機會我","createTime":"2019-02-09T09:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T13:08:15.000Z","uid":4661,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b2a2da19b789be96663da9e9983ceb40ce80f5d1","tid":1014561,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190208/large/1549623227_76da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F1549623227_76da.jpg&h=85a99c31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從蘇拿利坐正成為皇家馬德里教頭之後，西班牙國腳就失去了正選，只能在西班牙盃等較為次要的賽事上陣。無得踢當然心情不好，艾斯高今日在twitter吐苦水，指自己未受到公平對待，但仍會繼續努力操練，務求博得教練注意。<br />\n<br />\n就艾斯高的情況，前皇馬中場迪拿列特未有寄予同情，更說：「皇馬是一間不會等人的球會。達到標準的人就可以獲得上陣機會，不同資格的人就會被淘汰。」面對前輩的一番言論，艾斯高在twitter發文回應，強調自己未受公平對待，「我完全同意迪拿列特的講法，但當你等不到與隊友同等的機會，事情就變得不一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n當然艾斯高也「戴定頭盔」，強調自己會繼續努力爭取上陣機會，「雖然如此，我仍會繼續努力參與訓練，等待機會的到來！Hala Madrid！」不過與其在隊浪費光陰，艾斯高不如試下衝出西班牙，說不定可以再闖高峰。"},{"pid":"0c0a2803d57f35176eb92165f5e19deee88e8ddf","tid":1014561,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:52:41.000Z","msg":"阿狗如果用奧燒同你換ok?<br />\n你肯唔肯"},{"pid":"91855af09d2b576af5ca78563c46f029cad5cadd","tid":1014561,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:22:31.000Z","msg":"Welcome to Manchester United <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4267c40c643446f3f839f55d328d63da8a39fdd4","tid":1014561,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91855af09d2b576af5ca78563c46f029cad5cadd","tid":1014561,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:22:31.000Z","msg":"Welcome to Manchester United 